Narrator:
Here at Camp Pendleton,

00:37:10.828 --> 00:37:12.763
Marine families can send
their children

00:37:12.763 --> 00:37:16.934
to high quality on-base
child development centers.

00:37:16.934 --> 00:37:19.503
And not just at Camp Pendleton.

00:37:19.503 --> 00:37:22.707
The same is available to
every branch of the military,

00:37:22.707 --> 00:37:26.944
to all military personnel
regardless of rank.

