Man:
We looked at everything

00:37:33.217 --> 00:37:36.087
from a nanny to a daycare
out in town.

00:37:36.087 --> 00:37:37.688
We wouldn't have been
able to afford it.

00:37:37.688 --> 00:37:39.457
Our non-military friends,

00:37:39.457 --> 00:37:42.260
they're amazed that we only
pay what we pay.

