Narrator:
Childcare workers

00:37:51.202 --> 00:37:53.271
receive continuous training

00:37:53.271 --> 00:37:56.207
and here they are paid
about 50% more

00:37:56.207 --> 00:37:58.909
than the national
civilian median.

00:37:58.909 --> 00:38:00.311
Woman:
We also have our

00:38:00.311 --> 00:38:02.947
child assessment portfolio.

00:38:02.947 --> 00:38:06.383
And we communicate daily
with our parents.

