Are you guys all going
down for naps?

00:38:11.822 --> 00:38:13.090
Narrator:
All centers undergo

00:38:13.090 --> 00:38:14.792
regular surprise inspections.

00:38:14.792 --> 00:38:17.395
And most all are accredited.

00:38:17.395 --> 00:38:19.630
Here we go.
Would you like to be covered?

00:38:19.630 --> 00:38:21.724
Narrator:
But it wasn't always this way.

00:38:23.768 --> 00:38:26.504
In 1982, a scathing report

00:38:26.504 --> 00:38:28.506
found that
the military's childcare

00:38:28.506 --> 00:38:30.633
was among the worst
in the nation.

00:38:35.112 --> 00:38:37.148
So in 1989,

00:38:37.148 --> 00:38:42.253
18 years after the CCDA would
have become law for civilians,

00:38:42.253 --> 00:38:46.155
Congress passed the Military
Child Care Act.

00:38:48.092 --> 00:38:51.095
Military childcare is now
widely recognized

00:38:51.095 --> 00:38:53.063
as among the best
in the nation.

