why not our civilian workforce

00:39:13.217 --> 00:39:16.187
which protects
our national prosperity

00:39:16.187 --> 00:39:19.523
and their children who will
advance our future health,

00:39:19.523 --> 00:39:21.025
equity and success?

00:39:21.025 --> 00:39:21.192
Big jump!

00:39:21.192 --> 00:39:22.493
Big jump!

